01:12:30,596 --> 01:12:32,513
So, we've got 24 hours.

1401
01:12:33,371 --> 01:12:35,509
We have til six PM tomorrow.

1402
01:12:35,509 --> 01:12:36,827
- Yeah.

1403
01:12:36,827 --> 01:12:38,760
- Okay, I really won't keep you then.

